                <lexicalForm>Lista a scelta singola contenente le aree d’intervento compatibilmente alla Natura selezionata, relativa ai metadati di OpenCUP. Individua le categorie omogenee con cui è possibile descrivere "l'oggetto progettuale" (n. 6 aree – Classificazione con relativi codici):
01 – Immobili
02 – Trasporti
03 – Ambiente ed energia
04 – Aree produttive
05 – Ricerca, ITC, formazione ed altro
06 – Servizi per la P.A. e per la collettività.</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>it</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Area_di_intervento</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Single-choice list containing the areas of intervention compatible with the selected Nature, relative to the OpenCUP metadata. Identify the homogeneous categories with which to describe the "project object" (6 areas – Classification with related codes):
01 – Real Estate
02 – Transportation
03 – Environment and Energy
04 – Production Areas
05 – Research, ICT, Training and Other
06 – Services for the Public Administration and the Community.</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>en</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
          </annotations>
        </iri>
