              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Status of the CUP attached to an administrative act for the financing/authorization of public investments, whose classification, reported in the CUP system registry, complies with the constraints set by the legislation, which establishes and regulates the spending program pursuant to which the act itself is issued (CIPE Resolution no. 63 of 26 November 2020).</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>en</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
