            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Strumento_di_programmazione</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Programming tool</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#PlainLiteral</datatype>
                <language>en</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Strumento_di_programmazione</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Strumento di attuazione per la gestione e l'allocazione delle risorse finanziarie con la finalità di realizzare obiettivi specifici sulla base di un determinato piano annuale o triennale.</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>it</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Strumento_di_programmazione</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>An implementation tool for managing and allocating financial resources to achieve specific objectives based on a specific annual or three-year plan.</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>en</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
          </annotations>
        </iri>
        <iri>
          <value>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Strumento_di_programmazione_libero</value>
          <annotations>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Strumento_di_programmazione_libero</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Strumento di programmazione libero</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>it</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Strumento_di_programmazione_libero</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Free programming tool</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>en</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Strumento_di_programmazione_libero</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Si tratta della sottocategoria residuale di strumento di programmazione e rappresenta il dettaglio descrittivo o il nome specifico dello strumento qualora non sia riconducibile a una categoria standard o necessiti di ulteriore specificazione. Consente all'utente di inserire testualmente il nome del piano, dell'accordo o del programma specifico e fornisce flessibilità al corredo informativo, permettendo di tracciare strumenti di programmazione locali o specifici che non rientrano nelle tipologie generali predefinite.</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>it</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Strumento_di_programmazione_libero</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>This is the residual subcategory of programming tools and represents the descriptive detail or specific name of the tool if it doesn't fit into a standard category or requires further specification. It allows the user to enter the name of the specific plan, agreement, or program and provides flexibility in the information set, allowing for the tracking of local or specific programming tools that don't fit into the predefined general typologies.</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>en</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
          </annotations>
        </iri>
        <iri>
          <value>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Subinvestimento_PNRR</value>
          <annotations>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Subinvestimento_PNRR</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Sub-investimento PNRR</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#PlainLiteral</datatype>
                <language>it</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Subinvestimento_PNRR</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>PNRR sub-investment</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#PlainLiteral</datatype>
                <language>en</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Subinvestimento_PNRR</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Articolazione di dettaglio della Tematica PNRR che identifica la specifica linea di finanziamento a cui il progetto è collegato; la sua selezione, obbligatoria per i progetti PNRR, definisce il perimetro operativo dell'intervento e vincola la scelta dei Target PNRR di progetto ai soli obiettivi associati a quella specifica misura.</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>it</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Subinvestimento_PNRR</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Detailed breakdown of the PNRR Theme that identifies the specific funding line to which the project is linked; its selection, mandatory for PNRR projects, defines the operational scope of the intervention and limits the choice of PNRR project targets to the objectives associated with that specific measure.</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>en</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
          </annotations>
        </iri>
        <iri>
          <value>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Target_PNRR</value>
          <annotations>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Target_PNRR</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Target PNRR</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>it</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Target_PNRR</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>PNRR Target</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>en</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Target_PNRR</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Rappresenta l'obiettivo quantitativo o qualitativo (milestone/target) definito a livello nazionale per un determinato Sub-investimento PNRR; funge da parametro di riferimento per misurare l'avanzamento del Piano e costituisce il nodo a cui si agganciano i singoli Target PNRR di progetto per la rendicontazione dei risultati.</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>it</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Target_PNRR</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>It represents the quantitative or qualitative objective (milestone/target) defined at the national level for a specific PNRR sub-investment; it serves as a benchmark for measuring the Plan's progress and constitutes the hub to which the individual PNRR project targets are linked for reporting results.</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>en</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
          </annotations>
        </iri>
        <iri>
          <value>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Target_PNRR_di_progetto</value>
          <annotations>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Target_PNRR_di_progetto</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Target PNRR di progetto</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>it</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Target_PNRR_di_progetto</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>PNRR project targets</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>en</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Target_PNRR_di_progetto</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Costituisce la quota parte dell'obiettivo nazionale (Target PNRR) che il singolo Progetto di Investimento Pubblico si impegna a realizzare; è il valore specifico inserito nel corredo informativo del CUP che permette di verificare il contributo puntuale del progetto al raggiungimento dei traguardi previsti dal monitoraggio europeo.</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>it</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Target_PNRR_di_progetto</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>This represents the share of the national objective (PNRR Target) that each Public Investment Project commits to achieving; it is the specific value included in the CUP information package that allows verification of the project's specific contribution to achieving the goals set by European monitoring.</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>en</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
          </annotations>
        </iri>
        <iri>
          <value>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tematica_PNRR</value>
          <annotations>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tematica_PNRR</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Tematica PNRR</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>it</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tematica_PNRR</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>PNRR Theme</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>en</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tematica_PNRR</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Campo del corredo informativo del Progetto di investimento pubblico che identifica l'area strategica dell'intervento, obbligatorio per i progetti che beneficiano di fondi PNRR; la sua compilazione comporta l'attivazione automatica dei campi relativi al Sub-investimento e ai Target di progetto per il monitoraggio europeo.</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>it</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tematica_PNRR</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>This field in the Public Investment Project information package identifies the strategic area of ​​intervention, mandatory for projects receiving PNRR funding. Completing this field automatically activates the fields for Sub-investment and Project Targets for European monitoring.</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>en</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
          </annotations>
        </iri>
        <iri>
          <value>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tipo_area_soggetto_accreditato</value>
          <annotations>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tipo_area_soggetto_accreditato</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Tipo area soggetto accreditato</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#PlainLiteral</datatype>
                <language>it</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tipo_area_soggetto_accreditato</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Type of accredited subject area</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#PlainLiteral</datatype>
                <language>en</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tipo_area_soggetto_accreditato</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Campo che definisce l’ambito di competenza funzionale o settoriale prevalente del Soggetto accreditato al Sistema CUP (es. Sanità, Istruzione, Trasporti). Permette al sistema di associare il Soggetto ai rispettivi settori di intervento e agevola i flussi di monitoraggio verso le amministrazioni centrali competenti per materia.</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>it</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tipo_area_soggetto_accreditato</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>This field defines the primary functional or sectoral area of ​​expertise of the entity accredited to the CUP System (e.g., Healthcare, Education, Transportation). It allows the system to associate the entity with its respective sectors of intervention and facilitates monitoring flows to the central administrations responsible for the relevant subject matter.</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>en</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
          </annotations>
        </iri>
        <iri>
          <value>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tipo_categoria_soggetto_accreditato</value>
          <annotations>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tipo_categoria_soggetto_accreditato</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Tipo categoria soggetto accreditato</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#PlainLiteral</datatype>
                <language>it</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tipo_categoria_soggetto_accreditato</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Accredited subject category type</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#PlainLiteral</datatype>
                <language>en</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tipo_categoria_soggetto_accreditato</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Campo del corredo informativo che definisce il macro-settore di appartenenza del Soggetto accreditato al Sistema CUP (es. Amministrazioni Centrali, Enti Locali, Società Pubbliche). Rappresenta il primo livello di classificazione del Soggetto e determina l’ambito istituzionale in cui l’ente opera all'interno dell'Anagrafe Soggetti.</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>it</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tipo_categoria_soggetto_accreditato</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>This information field defines the macro-sector to which the entity accredited to the CUP System belongs (e.g., Central Administrations, Local Authorities, Public Companies). It represents the first level of entity classification and determines the institutional context in which the entity operates within the Register of Individuals.</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>en</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
          </annotations>
        </iri>
        <iri>
          <value>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tipo_di_finalità_partecipazione_conferimento</value>
          <annotations>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tipo_di_finalità_partecipazione_conferimento</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Tipo di finalità partecipazione conferimento</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#PlainLiteral</datatype>
                <language>it</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tipo_di_finalità_partecipazione_conferimento</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Type of purpose participation contribution</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#PlainLiteral</datatype>
                <language>en</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tipo_di_finalità_partecipazione_conferimento</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Campo del corredo informativo, attivato esclusivamente per i progetti con Natura "Sottoscrizione iniziale o aumento di capitale sociale (compresi spin off), fondi di rischio o di garanzia", che specifica lo scopo istituzionale o economico dell'operazione finanziaria. Serve a distinguere se il conferimento di capitale o la creazione di un fondo sia finalizzato al sostegno di attività produttive, alla ricerca e sviluppo (spin-off) o alla gestione di rischi finanziari.</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>it</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tipo_di_finalità_partecipazione_conferimento</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>This field in the information package, activated exclusively for projects with the "Initial subscription or increase in share capital (including spin-offs), venture or guarantee funds" nature, specifies the institutional or economic purpose of the financial transaction. It is used to distinguish whether the capital injection or the creation of a fund is intended to support production activities, research and development (spin-offs), or financial risk management.</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>en</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
          </annotations>
        </iri>
        <iri>
          <value>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tipo_motivazione_assenza_CUP_di_progettazione</value>
          <annotations>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tipo_motivazione_assenza_CUP_di_progettazione</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Tipo motivazione assenza CUP di progettazione</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>it</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tipo_motivazione_assenza_CUP_di_progettazione</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Type of reason for absence of CUP planning</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>en</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tipo_motivazione_assenza_CUP_di_progettazione</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Insieme delle causali selezionabili nel sistema per giustificare la mancata associazione di un cup di progettazione con Natura 2 ad un cup di Natura 3</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>it</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tipo_motivazione_assenza_CUP_di_progettazione</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Set of reasons that can be selected in the system to justify the failure to associate a Nature 2 design CUP with a Nature 3 CUP</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>en</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
          </annotations>
        </iri>
        <iri>
          <value>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tipo_natura_giuridica_soggetto_accreditato</value>
          <annotations>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tipo_natura_giuridica_soggetto_accreditato</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Tipo natura giuridica soggetto accreditato</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#PlainLiteral</datatype>
                <language>it</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tipo_natura_giuridica_soggetto_accreditato</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Type of legal nature of accredited entity</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#PlainLiteral</datatype>
                <language>en</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tipo_natura_giuridica_soggetto_accreditato</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Attributo che identifica la veste legale del Soggetto accreditato al Sistema CUP (es. Ente Pubblico Economico, Organo Costituzionale, Società per Azioni). Questo dato è fondamentale per definire le norme di diritto (pubblico o privato) a cui l'ente è soggetto e, conseguentemente, le sue facoltà nell'ambito dei procedimenti di spesa.</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>it</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tipo_natura_giuridica_soggetto_accreditato</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Attribute that identifies the legal status of the entity accredited to the CUP system (e.g., Public Economic Entity, Constitutional Body, Joint Stock Company). This information is essential for defining the legal provisions (public or private) to which the entity is subject and, consequently, its powers in the context of spending procedures.</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>en</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
          </annotations>
        </iri>
        <iri>
          <value>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tipo_sottocategoria_soggetto_accreditato</value>
          <annotations>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tipo_sottocategoria_soggetto_accreditato</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Tipo sottocategoria soggetto accreditato</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#PlainLiteral</datatype>
                <language>it</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tipo_sottocategoria_soggetto_accreditato</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Accredited entity subcategory type</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#PlainLiteral</datatype>
                <language>en</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tipo_sottocategoria_soggetto_accreditato</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Elemento di dettaglio che specifica ulteriormente la Categoria di appartenenza del Soggetto accreditato al Sistema CUP per una profilazione più precisa (es. all'interno della categoria "Enti Locali", distingue tra Comuni, Province o Città Metropolitane). Serve a raggruppare i soggetti per affinità di funzioni amministrative e competenze territoriali.</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>it</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tipo_sottocategoria_soggetto_accreditato</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>A detailed element that further specifies the Category to which the CUP System-accredited entity belongs for more precise profiling (e.g., within the "Local Authorities" category, it distinguishes between Municipalities, Provinces, or Metropolitan Cities). It serves to group entities by similarity of administrative functions and territorial competences.</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>en</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
          </annotations>
        </iri>
        <iri>
          <value>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tipo_strumento_di_programmazione</value>
          <annotations>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tipo_strumento_di_programmazione</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Tipo strumento di programmazione</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>it</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tipo_strumento_di_programmazione</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Programming tool type</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>en</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tipo_strumento_di_programmazione</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Si tratta di una sottocategoria di strumento di programmazione che si basa su un elenco predefinito (dominio di valori) fornito dal sistema CUP. Identifica la natura giuridico-amministrativa dell'atto di programmazione e permette l'aggregazione statistica dei dati e il monitoraggio a livello nazionale, facilitando il confronto tra programmi simili.</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>it</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tipo_strumento_di_programmazione</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>This is a subcategory of programming tools based on a predefined list (value domain) provided by the CUP system. It identifies the legal-administrative nature of the programming act and allows for statistical data aggregation and monitoring at the national level, facilitating comparisons between similar programs.</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>en</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
          </annotations>
        </iri>
        <iri>
          <value>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tipologia_copertura_finanziaria</value>
          <annotations>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tipologia_copertura_finanziaria</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Tipologia copertura finanziaria</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>it</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tipologia_copertura_finanziaria</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Type of financial coverage</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>en</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tipologia_copertura_finanziaria</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Campo obbligatorio del corredo informativo che identifica le fonti economiche destinate al Progetto d'investimento pubblico, permettendo l'associazione di più valori (pubblici, privati o propri) tramite un sistema di inserimento multiplo. La sua compilazione è governata da logiche di esclusività dipendenti dal campo "Partenariato Pubblico-Privato": se il partenariato è assente, sono ammesse solo fonti pubbliche; se è totale, solo fonti private; se è parziale, il sistema consente l'integrazione di entrambe le tipologie di risorse. Funge da filtro di validazione per assicurare che la struttura finanziaria dichiarata sia coerente con la forma contrattuale dell'investimento.</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>it</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tipologia_copertura_finanziaria</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>This mandatory field in the information package identifies the financial sources allocated to the public investment project, allowing the association of multiple values ​​(public, private, or own) through a multiple entry system. Its compilation is governed by exclusivity criteria based on the "Public-Private Partnership" field: if there is no partnership, only public sources are permitted; if there is a full partnership, only private sources are permitted; if there is a partial partnership, the system allows the integration of both types of resources. It serves as a validation filter to ensure that the declared financial structure is consistent with the contractual form of the investment.</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>en</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
          </annotations>
        </iri>
        <iri>
          <value>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tipologia_di_intervento</value>
          <annotations>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tipologia_di_intervento</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Tipologia di intervento</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#PlainLiteral</datatype>
                <language>it</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tipologia_di_intervento</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Type of intervention</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#PlainLiteral</datatype>
                <language>en</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tipologia_di_intervento</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Identifica con maggior livello di dettaglio la Natura di intervento e serve a specificare il metodo di attuazione. Ad esempio, nel caso di Natura 01 - Acquisto di beni, le Tipologie di intervento saranno "Nuova fornitura", "Manutenzione straordinaria" o "Altro").</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>it</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Tipologia_di_intervento</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>It identifies the nature of the intervention in greater detail and serves to specify the implementation method. For example, in the case of Nature 01 - Purchase of goods, the types of intervention will be "New supply", "Extraordinary maintenance", or "Other").</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>en</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
          </annotations>
        </iri>
        <iri>
          <value>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Unità_organizzativa</value>
