                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>en</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Utente_riferimento_cup</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Persona fisica, variabile nel tempo, che si è registrata al sistema come utente generatore e che interagisce con il sistema CUP per informazioni o per la manutenzione del corredo informativo di progetti attivi. Fa capo al Soggetto responsabile (Soggetto Titolare).</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>it</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Utente_riferimento_cup</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>A natural person, variable over time, who has registered in the system as a generator user and who interacts with the CUP system for information or to maintain the information set of active projects. This person reports to the Responsible Entity (Controller Entity).</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>en</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
          </annotations>
        </iri>
        <iri>
          <value>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Utente_sistema_cup</value>
          <annotations>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Utente_sistema_cup</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Utente sistema cup</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#PlainLiteral</datatype>
                <language>it</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Utente_sistema_cup</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Cup system user</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#PlainLiteral</datatype>
                <language>en</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Utente_sistema_cup</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>Persona fisica che, in seguito ad una procedura di accreditamento, interagisce con il sistema CUP. Può accreditarsi come “generatore“, se, oltre ad interrogare la banca dati, è interessato a richiedere codici ed effettuare le relative operazioni collegate, o come “lettore“, se ha solo l’esigenza di visualizzare il contenuto della banca dati del sistema.</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>it</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://w3id.org/italia/onto/OpenCUP/Utente_sistema_cup</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>A natural person who, following an accreditation procedure, interacts with the CUP system. They can register as a "generator" if, in addition to querying the database, they are interested in requesting codes and performing related operations, or as a "reader" if they only need to view the contents of the system's database.</lexicalForm>
                <datatype>None</datatype>
                <language>en</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
          </annotations>
        </iri>
